      "value": "What are Preloading and Prefetching?"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Preloading and prefetching are techniques used to load resources in advance to improve performance and user experience."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Difference Between Preload and Prefetch"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "value": {
        "headers": ["Feature", "Preload", "Prefetch"],
